title: Has anyone ordered car wheel or car alloy watches from Alibaba?
selftext:
I was recently scrolling through Instagram and came across an account selling car wheel watches, Instragram name : TOCG Watches for 8000 INR and RSChrono Watches for the same price. When I searched on Google, I found the same watches on Alibaba for 5-10 bucks, and they even showed me the watches in a live video call.

I'm curious if anyone here has ordered similar watches from Alibaba. I have some doubts about the authenticity and quality. Is it possible to import these watches in bulk and sell them for a lower cost in India?

Also, does anyone know if TOCG Watches and RSChrono Watches originate from China? Any insights would be appreciated!


#watch
comments: You can get a decent gshock that will last you 10 years easily for this money.
